title: MisterMusic Show 342 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 342 [2 hours] 192kbps Mp3-


New music this week from Them Are Us Too, and Man Without Country.
Plus a big hit from February 1969 is the 'Oldie of the Week'.
It's a blend of indie, alternative music with over 5 decades of classic hits.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
